import React from "react"; import {ProgressBar} from 'primereact/progressbar'; class Rates extends React.Component{ render(){ const {highestactive,highestrecovered,highestdeaths} = this.context.data; return(
Highest Active Rate
{highestactive.name} {highestactive.active_percentage.toFixed(2)}%




Highest Recovery Rate
{highestrecovered.name.split(" ")[0]} {highestrecovered.rec_percentage.toFixed(2)}%




Highest Death Rate
{highestdeaths.name} {highestdeaths.death_percentage.toFixed(2)}%
) } } export default Rates;
